<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - BOOKIFYSTAY</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa; /* Clean light grey background */
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        }
        .custom-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 0.5rem 1rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border: none;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            height: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container py-5">
    
    <div class="mb-4">
        <a href="/listing" class="btn btn-outline-dark rounded-pill px-4 fw-bold">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-2"></i> Back to Home
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3 text-dark">About <span class="text-primary">BOOKIFYSTAY</span></h1>
        <p class="lead text-muted mx-auto" style="max-width: 700px;">
            A full-stack booking marketplace built to seamlessly connect travelers with unique accommodations.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center">
        
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-5">
            <div class="custom-card text-center d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
                <h2 class="h3 fw-bold mb-1 text-dark">Vardan Singh</h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-4 fs-5">Full-Stack Developer</p>
                
                <div class="d-grid gap-3 mt-2">
                    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/vardan-singh-b86a0a363/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill fw-bold py-2">
                        <i class="fab fa-linkedin me-2"></i> LinkedIn Profile
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://github.com/vardan-18" target="_blank" class="btn btn-dark rounded-pill fw-bold py-2">
                        <i class="fab fa-github me-2"></i> GitHub Profile
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-7">
            <div class="custom-card">
                <h3 class="fw-bold mb-4 border-bottom pb-3 text-dark">The Project Story</h3>
                
                <p class="fs-5 text-secondary" style="line-height: 1.7;">
                    BOOKIFYSTAY was developed as a comprehensive showcase project to demonstrate modern web development practices and database architecture. 
                </p>
                
                <p class="text-secondary mb-5" style="line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                    This platform features a complete two-sided marketplace, allowing users to browse dynamic listings, make real-time booking requests, and interact through a host/guest dashboard system. It handles secure user authentication, automated email confirmations, dynamic price calculations, and robust server-side routing.
                </p>
                
                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-dark">Tech Stack Used</h4>
                <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <span class="badge rounded-pill bg-primary px-3 py-2 fs-6">Node.js</span>
                    <span class="badge rounded-pill bg-dark px-3 py-2 fs-6">Express.js</span>
                    <span class="badge rounded-pill bg-success px-3 py-2 fs-6">MongoDB</span>
                    <span class="badge rounded-pill bg-danger px-3 py-2 fs-6">Mongoose</span>
                    <span class="badge rounded-pill text-dark px-3 py-2 fs-6" style="background-color: #ffc107;">EJS</span>
                    <span class="badge rounded-pill bg-info text-dark px-3 py-2 fs-6">Bootstrap 5</span>
                    <span class="badge rounded-pill bg-secondary px-3 py-2 fs-6">Nodemailer</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>